{"tag":"section","attrib":{"id":"idc9f17a98-3a70-11f1-bde1-a5140e158598","identifier":"/us/usc/t43/s564"},"text":null,"children":[{"tag":"num","attrib":{"value":"564"},"text":"§ 564.","children":[],"tail":null},{"tag":"heading","attrib":{},"text":" Reappraisal of town lots for sale","children":[],"tail":null},{"tag":"content","attrib":{},"text":"\n","children":[{"tag":"p","attrib":{},"text":"The Secretary of the Interior is authorized, whenever he may deem it necessary, to reappraise all unsold lots within town sites on proj­ects under the reclamation Act heretofore or hereafter appraised under the provisions of sections 562 and 563 of this title; and thereafter to proceed with the sale of such town lots in accordance with said sections.","children":[],"tail":"\n"}],"tail":null},{"tag":"sourceCredit","attrib":{"id":"idc9f17a99-3a70-11f1-bde1-a5140e158598"},"text":"(","children":[{"tag":"ref","attrib":{"href":"/us/act/1910-06-11/ch284/s1"},"text":"June 11, 1910, ch. 284, § 1","children":[],"tail":", "},{"tag":"ref","attrib":{"href":"/us/stat/36/465"},"text":"36 Stat. 465","children":[],"tail":".)"}],"tail":"\n"},{"tag":"notes","attrib":{"type":"uscNote","id":"idc9f17a9a-3a70-11f1-bde1-a5140e158598"},"text":"\n","children":[{"tag":"note","attrib":{"role":"crossHeading","topic":"editorialNotes","id":"idc9f17a9b-3a70-11f1-bde1-a5140e158598"},"text":null,"children":[{"tag":"heading","attrib":{},"text":null,"children":[{"tag":"b","attrib":{},"text":"Editorial Notes","children":[],"tail":null}],"tail":null}],"tail":"\n"},{"tag":"note","attrib":{"topic":"referencesInText","id":"idc9f17a9c-3a70-11f1-bde1-a5140e158598"},"text":"\n","children":[{"tag":"heading","attrib":{},"text":"References in Text","children":[],"tail":null},{"tag":"p","attrib":{},"text":"The reclamation Act, referred to in text, probably means ","children":[{"tag":"ref","attrib":{"href":"/us/act/1902-06-17/ch1093"},"text":"act June 17, 1902, ch. 1093","children":[],"tail":", "},{"tag":"ref","attrib":{"href":"/us/stat/32/388"},"text":"32 Stat. 388","children":[],"tail":", popularly known as the Reclamation Act, which is classified generally to this chapter. For complete classification of this Act to the Code, see Short Title note set out under "},{"tag":"ref","attrib":{"href":"/us/usc/t43/s371"},"text":"section 371 of this title","children":[],"tail":" and Tables."}],"tail":"\n"}],"tail":"\n"}],"tail":"\n"}],"tail":null}
